'''螺紋緊固件'''（Threaded fastener）是一種有內[[螺紋|螺紋]]或是外螺紋的機械零件，一般會作為[[緊固件|緊固件]]使用，方便多個組件的組合<ref>{{Citation | last = Groover | first = Mikell P. | title = Fundamentals of Modern Manufacturing: Materials, Processes, and Systems | page = 767 | publisher = John Wiley and Sons | year = 2010 | edition = 4th | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=QU-Qvud3OvoC&pg=PA767 | isbn = 978-0-470-46700-8 | postscript =.}}</ref>。

最常見的螺紋緊固件是[[螺絲|螺絲]]、[[螺帽|螺帽]]及[[螺栓|螺栓]]。不過也有其他的螺紋緊固件，例如[[浮动螺母|浮动螺母]]、{{le|螺紋插件|Threaded insert}}、{{le|螺紋桿|threaded rod}}等。

